summary: ...PRISCILLA BRINGING HIGH SURF AND GUSTY WINDS TO THE PACIFIC COAST OF BAJA CALIFORNIA SUR... ...MOISTURE FROM PRISCILLA WILL INCREASE THE RISK OF FLOODING ACROSS THE U.S. DESERT SOUTHWEST LATE THIS WEEK THROUGH THE WEEKEND...
